column2: SELECT TOP # s1.objID as s1, s2.objID as s2, s1.u as u1, s2.u as u2, s1.r as r1, s2.r as r2, s1.err_u as err_u1, s2.err_u as err_u2, s1.err_r as  err_r1, s2.err_r as err_r2, N.distance as dist  FROM Star AS S1   JOIN Neighbors AS N ON S1.objID = N.objID   JOIN Star AS S2 ON S2.objID = N.NeighborObjID   WHERE   N.NeighborType = dbo.fPhotoType(&&&)  N.Type = dbo.fPhotoType(&&&)  GROUP BY S1.objID
